  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the future of competitive sports!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Puzzle fans rejoice!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/2930c9760c3589251b037785c4419988.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/2930c9760c3589251b037785c4419988.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/2930c9760c3589251b037785c4419988.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make matches by destroying or swapping gems. Can you make a Mega Match (9)!?<br><br></li><li><strong>Defend your towers from the enemy's ranks.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/4346f9fb1e886a3bf2789ae00c551b95.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/4346f9fb1e886a3bf2789ae00c551b95.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/4346f9fb1e886a3bf2789ae00c551b95.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Whether it's KBaM or a controller, your shooting skills will be put to the test.<br><br></li><li><strong>RTS-inspired economy system.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/69ade178b11da99a12d0685d0ad632da.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/69ade178b11da99a12d0685d0ad632da.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/69ade178b11da99a12d0685d0ad632da.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hire peons to mine for bolts.  Use bolts to purchase items of increasing power!<br><br></li><li><strong>Research, buy items, and adapt to game-changing events - all in <i>real time</i>.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/f944fccac479d3471132e0ee99abf054.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/f944fccac479d3471132e0ee99abf054.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/f944fccac479d3471132e0ee99abf054.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each match3+ sends a minion down a chosen lane: Top, Bottom, Mid, and Jungle.<br>Keep an eye on your opponent and adapt accordingly!<br><br></li><li><strong>Gem Frenzy Mode.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/89afbe36d5a193be0c674e22b4175aea.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/89afbe36d5a193be0c674e22b4175aea.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/89afbe36d5a193be0c674e22b4175aea.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The fastest matcher wins!  In Gem Frenzy, don't worry about towers, minions, items, or sniping.  Focus on making matches and race to victory!<br><br></li><li><strong>Background on me and the game.</strong><br>Match Match Mania! was inspired by games in the late 90s and early 2000s - Weird ideas mashed together and just going for it.  Inspirations include Yoshi's Cookie, Power Stone, Chu Chu Rocket, and much, much more.<br>The game was developed with split-screen, human vs human competitive play in mind.  If you don't have anyone at home, try Steam Remote Play to invite a friend!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to the future of competitive sports!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Puzzle fans rejoice!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/2930c9760c3589251b037785c4419988.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/2930c9760c3589251b037785c4419988.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/2930c9760c3589251b037785c4419988.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make matches by destroying or swapping gems. Can you make a Mega Match (9)!?<br><br></li><li><strong>Defend your towers from the enemy's ranks.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/4346f9fb1e886a3bf2789ae00c551b95.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/4346f9fb1e886a3bf2789ae00c551b95.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/4346f9fb1e886a3bf2789ae00c551b95.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Whether it's KBaM or a controller, your shooting skills will be put to the test.<br><br></li><li><strong>RTS-inspired economy system.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/69ade178b11da99a12d0685d0ad632da.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/69ade178b11da99a12d0685d0ad632da.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/69ade178b11da99a12d0685d0ad632da.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hire peons to mine for bolts.  Use bolts to purchase items of increasing power!<br><br></li><li><strong>Research, buy items, and adapt to game-changing events - all in <i>real time</i>.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/f944fccac479d3471132e0ee99abf054.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/f944fccac479d3471132e0ee99abf054.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/f944fccac479d3471132e0ee99abf054.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each match3+ sends a minion down a chosen lane: Top, Bottom, Mid, and Jungle.<br>Keep an eye on your opponent and adapt accordingly!<br><br></li><li><strong>Gem Frenzy Mode.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/89afbe36d5a193be0c674e22b4175aea.poster.avif?t=1667318737\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/89afbe36d5a193be0c674e22b4175aea.webm?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354270/extras/89afbe36d5a193be0c674e22b4175aea.mp4?t=1667318737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The fastest matcher wins!  In Gem Frenzy, don't worry about towers, minions, items, or sniping.  Focus on making matches and race to victory!<br><br></li><li><strong>Background on me and the game.</strong><br>Match Match Mania! was inspired by games in the late 90s and early 2000s - Weird ideas mashed together and just going for it.  Inspirations include Yoshi's Cookie, Power Stone, Chu Chu Rocket, and much, much more.<br>The game was developed with split-screen, human vs human competitive play in mind.  If you don't have anyone at home, try Steam Remote Play to invite a friend!</li></ul>",
